headline: ADP National Employment Report Preliminary Estimate December 27, 2025
summary: For the four weeks ending December 27, 2025, U.S. private employers added an average of 8,000 jobs per week, according to the NER Pulse, a weekly update of the monthly ADP National Employment Report (NER).
